PBN is a computer version of the Paint By Numbers puzzle game
created by Non Ishida for London's Sunday Telegraph and popularized in
the USA by Games magazine.

------------------------------------------------------------------

The pbnsolve program allows you to solve a previously-created puzzle.

Run

	pbnsolve puzzles/0.pbn

and select the "Help" menu button to get started.

------------------------------------------------------------------

The pbncreate program allows you to create a new puzzle. It is also
described in the help file.
